As a user(customer) 
I want to be able to search the necessary item
So that I can faster make a purchase 

Scope

The searching functionality
The item card
It should work in Chrome, Mozilla, Safari browsers
It should also work in Mobile


Precondition:

The searching functionality is implemented


Acceptance criteria:


Scenario 1:User can successfully find the necessary item 
Given: User on the "Shop" page
When: Click on the "Search" field
And: Enter a valid name of the item
And: Click the "Search" button
Then: The item is founded



Scenario 1: The user can successfully find the item 
Given: User on the "Shop" page
When: Click on the "Search" field
And: Enter an invalid name of the item
And: Click the "Search" button
Then: The warring message is shown









